cens]]'' <small>Joy Thomps.</small> - Qld \n*''[[Leptospermum recurvum]]'' <small>Hook.f.</small> - Sabah, Sulawesi \n*''[[Leptospermum riparium]]'' <small>[[Dennis Ivor Morris|D.I.Morris]]</small> - Tas \n*''[[Leptospermum roei]]'' <small>[[George Bentham|Benth.]]</small> - WA\n*''[[Leptospermum rotundifolium]]'' <small>(Maiden & Betche) [[Frederick Arthur Rodway|F.A.Rodway]]</small> - NSW\n*''[[Leptospermum rupestre]]'' <small>Hook.f.</small> - Tas\n*''[[Leptospermum rupicola]]'' <small>Joy Thomps.</small> - NSW \n*''[[Leptospermum scoparium]]'' <small>[[J.R.Forst.]] & [[G.Forst.]]</small> -  Vic, NSW, Tas, NZ \n*''[[Leptospermum sejunctum]]'' <small>Joy Thomps.</small> - NSW \n*''[[Leptospermum semibaccatum]]'' <small>Cheel</small> - Qld, NSW \n*''[[Leptospermum sericatum]]'' <small>[[Lindl.]]</small> - Qld\n*''[[Leptospermum sericeum]]'' <small>[[Labill.]]</small> - WA\n*''[[Leptospermum speciosum]]'' <small>Schauer</small> - Qld, NSW\n*''[[Leptospermum spectabile]]'' <small>Joy Thomps.</small> - NSW\n*''[[Leptospermum sphaerocarpum]]'' <small>Cheel</small> - NSW  \n*''[[Leptospermum spinescens]]'' <small>[[Endl.]]</small> - WA\n*''[[Leptospermum squarrosum]]'' <small>Gaertn.</small> - NSW \n*''[[Leptospermum subglabratum]]'' <small>Joy Thomps.</small> - NSW \n*''[[Leptospermum subtenue]]'' <small>Joy Thomps.</small> - [[Western Australia|WA]] \n*''[[Leptospermum thompsonii]]'' <small>Joy Thomps.</small> - NSW  \n*''[[Leptospermum trinervium]]'' <small>(Sm.) Joy Thomps.</small> - Qld, NSW, Vic\n*''[[Leptospermum turbinatum]]'' <small>Joy Thomps.</small> - Vic\n*''[[Leptospermum variabile]]'' <small>Joy Thomps.</small> - Qld, NSW\n*''[[Leptospermum venustum]]'' <small>A.R.Bean</small> - Qld  \n*''[[Leptospermum whitei]]'' <small>Cheel</small> - Qld, NSW  \n*''[[Leptospermum wooroonooran]]'' <small>F.M.Bailey</small> - Qld\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Commons category-inline}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q135621}}\n\n[[Category:Leptospermum